videos.headline: Purdy's runs for 44 yards, throws a TD pass on next play
videos.description: Iowa State QB Brock Purdy runs 44 yards to the 1-yard line and throws a touchdown pass on the ensuing play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdy's runs for 44 yards, throws a TD pass on next play) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Cyclones' defense come up big with strip sack, TD
videos.description: Iowa State's O'Rien Vance hits TCU QB Max Duggan and forces the fumble, and Eyioma Uwazurike scoops it up for a Cyclones touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cyclones' defense come up big with strip sack, TD) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Purdy finds a wide-open Kolar for Cyclones TD
videos.description: Brock Purdy floats a pass over to Charlie Kolar for a 25-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdy finds a wide-open Kolar for Cyclones TD) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Purdy calls his own number on 10-yard score
videos.description: Brock Purdy drops back, fakes the pass and takes off for a 10-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Reagor snags TD catch over defender
videos.description: Max Duggan tosses it up to Jalen Reagor, who makes a great touchdown grab over the defender.
